title: [Macabre Masquerade, Atelier]
description: A web-like chandelier of blackened steel hangs above a many-horned glaes and ivory skeleton, casting fragmented shadows upon the ebonwood-planked floor.  The disjointed sounds of an onyx-framed musicbox plink randomly, the box nestled within a darkened corner with a pair of wire-framed mannequins.  A faint haze of incense smoke veils the air around the shop, the scent of absinthe and leather lingering as it dissipates.
